'''Allkpop'''是2007年10月30日在美国推出的[[韩国流行音乐|韩国流行音乐]]英文博客<ref>{{Cite news|title=Korean Pop, with Online Help, Goes Global|url=http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2013227,00.html|work=Time|date=26 August 2010|accessdate=2020-09-29|archive-date=2012-08-28|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AF8qppT5?url=http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2013227,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，总部设在美國[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]的{{link-en|埃奇沃特|Edgewater, New Jersey}}。

allkpop由其母公司6Theory Media拥有和运营，是[[流量|流量]]最大的[[韩国流行音乐|韩国流行音乐]]新闻网站之一，每月有超过750万读者<ref name="mashable2010">{{Cite web|title=Mashable Awards 2010: Announcing The Winners|url=http://mashable.com/2011/01/07/mashable-awards-2010-announcing-the-winners/|accessdate=22 July 2011|work=Mashable|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714045320/http://mashable.com/2011/01/07/mashable-awards-2010-announcing-the-winners/|archivedate=2011-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其文章经常被其他出版物引用，并通过社交媒体分享至世界各地<ref>{{Cite news|title=Psy and Google's Eric Schmidt get it on 'Gangnam Style'|url=https://www.latimes.com/business/technology/la-fi-tn-psy-eric-schmidt-gangnam-style-20120927,0,1267968.story|quote="AllKpop reports Google presented Psy with a framed Doodle of a dragon in return for the dance lesson."|work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]|accessdate=16 December 2012|first=Salvador|author=Rodriguez|date=27 September 2012|archive-date=2012-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121207060629/http://www.latimes.com/business/technology/la-fi-tn-psy-eric-schmidt-gangnam-style-20120927,0,1267968.story|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite magazine|title=Asiatischer Pop-Star in tödlichen Unfall verwickelt|url=http://www.spiegel.de/panorama/leute/twitter-hype-asiatischer-pop-star-in-toedlichen-unfall-verwickelt-a-765971.html|magazine=[[明镜|明镜]]|language=de|access-date=16 December 2012|quote="Die Produktionsfirma YG Entertainment, die die Band vertritt, betont laut der auf koreanischen Pop spezialisierten Musikwebsite www.allkpop.com, es sei ein sehr komplizierter Fall."|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125234603/https://www.spiegel.de/panorama/leute/twitter-hype-asiatischer-pop-star-in-toedlichen-unfall-verwickelt-a-765971.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Wonder Girls' Sunye Denies Getting Married Next Month|url=http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/374649/wonder-girls-sunye-denies-getting-married-next-month|accessdate=24 January 2013|author=Hicap|first=Johnathan|work=[[马尼拉公报|马尼拉公报]]|archive-date=2012-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927050500/http://www.mb.com.ph/articles/374649/wonder-girls-sunye-denies-getting-married-next-month|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=K-Pop Star Psy Will Get His Own 'Gangnam Style' Designer Clothing Line|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/psy-getting-gangnam-style-clothing-line-2012-9|accessdate=24 January 2013|author=Lutz|first=Ashley|work=[[商业内幕|商业内幕]]|quote=The news comes via a video (which perhaps will go viral a la Gangnam Style) that we found on K-Pop site AllKPop.com.|archive-date=2020-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614044537/https://www.businessinsider.com/psy-getting-gangnam-style-clothing-line-2012-9|dead-url=no}}</ref>。allkpop的新闻和文章都是根据最新发布的[[韩国流行音乐|韩国流行音乐]]新闻撰写的。[[韩国先驱报|韩国先驱报]]称allkpop为 "最快的[[韩国流行音乐|韩国流行音乐]]新闻发布者"<ref>{{Cite news|title=Click! Online gateways to Korea|url=http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20110225000672|work=[[韩国先驱报|韩国先驱报]]|accessdate=12 March 2013|quote=When it comes to K-pop, Allkpop.com (www.allkpop.com) is the fastest news breaker. Latest celebrity gossips and news draw over 3 million monthly readers worldwide and takes Hallyu to audiences beyond Asia.|archive-date=2018-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181027061532/http://nwww.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20110225000672|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

